{"lastModified":1775161606196,"uri":"c::28226710116::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Florida, Bahamas\n\nThe 2016 Azimut 68 Fly is a stunning Italian luxury yacht that combines sleek design, powerful performance, and exceptional comfort. With her commanding presence and spacious layout, she is perfectly suited for both day cruising in Miami and extended adventures to the Keys or the Bahamas. Powered by twin MAN engines, the Azimut 68 delivers impressive speed, smooth handling, and a refined cruising experience.\n\nHer expansive flybridge is a true highlight, offering a helm station, wet bar, al fresco dining, and multiple lounging areas with sweeping views, ideal for entertaining or relaxing under the sun. The aft deck provides seamless indoor-outdoor living, while the bow lounge features oversized sunpads for ultimate comfort at sea.\n\nInside, the yacht showcases Azimut’s signature contemporary style, with a bright salon, elegant dining space, and a fully equipped galley. Large windows flood the interior with natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. Below deck, she offers 4 luxurious staterooms, including a full-beam master suite with ensuite bathroom, providing privacy and comfort for overnight guests.\n\nBlending Italian sophistication with versatile layouts, the 2016 Azimut 68 Fly is the perfect yacht for unforgettable experiences, from chic Miami day charters to multi-day escapes across turquoise Bahamian waters.\n\nSuggested Itinerary:\nEnjoy a custom departure from your preferred marina and set course for the scenic waterways of North Miami, where calm seas and vibrant sights await.\n\nMorning: Begin your cruise along the Intracoastal Waterway, passing the stunning waterfront neighborhoods of Bal Harbour, Sunny Isles, and Golden Beach. Lounge on the flybridge or the bow while soaking in the breeze and ocean views.\nMidday: Drop anchor at the iconic Haulover Sandbar, the perfect spot for swimming, lounging, and enjoying water toys like paddleboards or floaties in waist-deep turquoise water.\nAfternoon: Explore the nearby Oleta River State Park, cruise through mangrove-lined channels, or simply enjoy lunch and relaxation onboard in a peaceful setting away from the crowds.\nEvening: As golden hour approaches, enjoy a relaxed cruise along the coast. Toast to the sunset from the flybridge or aft deck as the city begins to light up in the distance.","blueprint":{"name":"LE GRAND BLEU","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d7a33240-6d85-11f0-a423-ddd5df0c4c09/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d7600ec1-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d79612e0-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d799bc60-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d793f000-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d760f920-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d797c090-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d7a1d2b0-6d85-11f0-bd45-97d2973fcc7f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d79883e0-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d799e370-6d85-11f0-a422-ddd5df0c4c09/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::005b4bb0-6d80-11f0-bf40-8d8e3ed549ca::assets::d7926960-6d85-11f0-9925-5d23fbee2e2a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::